word_mean_info__list.difference: 着重个人的天赋的才能或在某方面的显著本领，常暗含不能用一般规律作解释的意味。
语气最强，指天赋的高度才能与智力。
多指先天或后天习得的运用自如的能力，常暗示接受能力强，能迅速掌握一种学术训练或艺术技巧。
着重指人某方面具有可发展和倍养的突出天赋才能，但语意比genius弱。
侧重指人的潜在能力，通常不指体力，多指才智，尤指接受与领悟能力。
多用于人，指胜任某项具体工作的能力，也指本身具有、尚未发挥的潜在能力。常与of或for连用。
普通用词，指人先天的或学来的各种能力。
正式用词，侧重指令人满意的业务能力与水平，达到胜任某项工作等的要求。

bilingual.source: The faculty is meeting tomorrow at 10 a. m.
bilingual.target: 全体教员明天上午10点开会。

bilingual.source: This letter is circulating among the faculty.
bilingual.target: 这封信在全体教员中传递。

bilingual.source: The body of faculty and students of a university.
bilingual.target: 大学里全体教员和学生。

bilingual.source: No gray hair We were all tired after a difficult faculty meeting.
bilingual.target: 我们在一个乏味的全体教员会议之后全都很疲累。

bilingual.source: The whole faculty finally passes a decision to cancel the model test.
bilingual.target: 全体教员最终通过一项决议,取消模拟考试.

bilingual.source: A normal faculty in Chineses university is recognized by Australian Government.
bilingual.target: 常态中国的大学的全体教员被澳洲的政府辨认出。

bilingual.source: Alex, trustees, faculty and deans of the university, my fellow honorees, and especially you the class of 2015. Yes.
bilingual.target: 感谢亚历克斯、理事会、全体教员和院长、我的宾客们，尤其是你们，2015届的毕业生们。是的。

bilingual.source: Our students and faculty have embodied that spirit through their work to serve in our neighborhood and around the world.
bilingual.target: 我们的学生和全体教员在为邻居和整个世界提供帮助时都贯彻了这一点。

bilingual.source: The graduated student of restaurant faculty will encourage to open Jiangmen style restaurant across GuangDong to other province, to overseas.
bilingual.target: 餐馆全体教员的被毕业的学生将会鼓励对其他的省开放横过广东的江门风格餐馆，到在海外。

bilingual.source: Thank you, President Hennessy, and to thetrustees and the faculty, to all of the parents and grandparents, to you, the Stanford graduates.
bilingual.target: Hennessy校长，全体教员，家长，还有斯坦福的毕业生门，非常感谢你们。

list.abstract: faculty（英 [ˈfæklti]，美 [ˈfæklti]），英语单词，作名词为天赋；系；院；特许证；许可证。例句：Academics were brown-nosing the senior faculty.（学者们在拍高级教员的马屁。） 近义词有ability等。

yingyinNormal.en: The faculty were all telling him, maybe this isn't for you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 老师们都劝他，或许你真的不是搞音乐的料。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, the housekeeper in the faculty residence didn't speak any English.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当时学院公寓里的管家不会讲英文。

yingyinNormal.en: We are one school, one student body, one faculty! Can we not agree on that?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们是同一所学校，带着同一批学生的老师！这点应该都同意吧？

yingyinNormal.en: The faculty is completing midyear reviews. We're deciding which placement applications to support.
yingyinNormal.zh: 教员们正在写期中评语。我门正在决定支持哪一个就业工作。

yingyinNormal.en: Thought you might've forgotten me. Who was your faculty advisor at Stanford? What? In the computer science department.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我以为你忘了我了。你在斯坦福的时候导师是谁？什么？你在计算机系的时候。

yingyinNormal.en: Excuse me, the whole tenure system is ridiculous. A guaranteed job for life only encourages the faculty to become complacent.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拜托，终身教职制度本来就十分荒谬，一个终身有保障的工作只会让那些人变得过于自满，怠惰。

yingyinNormal.en: To president Faust, my fellow honorands, Carl, that was so beautiful, thank you so much, and James Rothenberg, Stephanie Wilson, Harvard faculty, with a special bow to my friend, Doctor Henry Louis Gates.
yingyinNormal.zh: 福斯特校长，以及各位荣誉学位获得者，卡尔，这一切是如此美好，非常感谢你们。还有詹姆斯·罗森伯格，斯蒂芬妮·威尔逊，以及哈佛大学教职员工，特别要向我的朋友亨利·路易斯·盖茨博士致敬。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a group of university departments concerned with a major division of knowledge

examination_example.sentence: Mary Yoke, PhD, a <highlight>faculty</highlight> member in the kinesiology department at Indiana University in Bloomington.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 玛丽·约克博士是布卢明顿印第安纳大学运动机能系的一名教员。

examination_example.sentence: If there is loss of a close apprenticeship relationship between <highlight>faculty</highlight> members and postgrarduate students, the student culture becomes the chief socializing force .
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果教师和研究生之间失去亲密的学徒关系，学生文化就会成为主要的社交力量。

examination_example.sentence: In the 1960s and 1970s, European universities saw marked changes in their governance arrangements, with the empowerment of junior <highlight>faculty</highlight> and to some degree of students as well.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在20世纪60年代和70年代，欧洲大学的治理安排发生了显著变化，年轻教员和一些的学生获得了权力。

sense_info_list.en: a department or group of related departments in a college or university

examination_example.sentence: When the new staff are predominantly young people fresh from postgraduate study, they largely define the norms of academic life in that <highlight>faculty</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当新员工主要是刚从研究生院毕业的年轻人时，他们在很大程度上定义了该学院学术生活的规范。

examination_example.sentence: There will be military training which is an opportunity to socialize with each other while further engaging with campus <highlight>faculty</highlight> and staff.

examination_example.sentence: This connection happens not only by means of collaborative development, review and testing, but also at conferences where <highlight>faculty</highlight> regularly decide on their textbooks and curricula for the coming year.
